    <h1>Ambush Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">A strategy where a brand creates association with a major event — Olympics, World Cup, Super Bowl — <strong>without being an official sponsor</strong>. Cheaper, riskier, and often more memorable than paid sponsorship.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
